{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureShield Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #0056b3; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #003d80 3px solid; /* Darker blue for contrast */\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #007bff; /* Brand blue */\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n        }\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.7), rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/0056b3/ffffff?text=Cybersecurity+Shield') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #007bff; /* Brand blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #0056b3;\n        }\n        .button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3; /* Darker blue on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #services h3, #about h3, #contact h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #0056b3; /* Brand blue */\n        }\n        .service-item, .about-content, .contact-info {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #007bff; /* Brand blue */\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #0056b3; /* Brand blue */\n        }\n        #contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        #contact input, #contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        #contact textarea {\n            height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #003d80; /* Darker blue */\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>SecureShield Cybersecurity</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#hero\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Digital Fortress in a Connected World</h2>\n            <p>Protecting your business from evolving cyber threats with cutting-edge solutions and expert guidance.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"button\">Get a Free Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Services</h3>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                <h4>Threat Detection & Prevention</h4>\n                <p>Proactive monitoring and advanced security measures to identify and neutralize threats before they impact your operations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lock\"></i>\n                <h4>Data Encryption & Protection</h4>\n                <p>Ensuring your sensitive data is secured with robust encryption and access control mechanisms.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-user-shield\"></i>\n                <h4>Security Audits & Compliance</h4>\n                <p>Comprehensive assessments of your security posture to ensure compliance with industry regulations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-network-wired\"></i>\n                <h4>Network Security</h4>\n                <p>Securing your network infrastructure against unauthorized access and malicious attacks.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>About SecureShield</h3>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>SecureShield Cybersecurity is dedicated to providing top-tier security solutions for businesses of all sizes. Our team of experienced professionals is committed to understanding your unique challenges and delivering tailored strategies to safeguard your digital assets. We believe in building trust through transparency, expertise, and unwavering dedication to your security.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p><i class=\"fas fa-phone\"></i> +1 (123) 456-7890</p>\n                <p><i class=\"fas fa-envelope\"></i> info@secureshield.com</p>\n                <p><i class=\"fas fa-map-marker-alt\"></i> 123 Cyber Lane, Tech City, TX 75001</p>\n            </div>\n            <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"button\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 SecureShield Cybersecurity. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(e) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch shortly.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}